For sale: Rifle Dynamics AK to M4 Stock Adapter. This allows you to use an AR style buffer tube and any AR stock you want, also it brings the stock more level with the rifle allowing better cheak weld. The following information is from the Rifle Dynamics site:
The Rifle Dynamics AK to M-4 Stock Adapter (Gen II) allows for the replacement of any standard fixed stock AKM (see exceptions below) to work with an AR buffer tube assembly. The angle of our adapter is designed specifically to position the buffer tube, allowing the shooter to easily access proper sight picture with iron sights and/or optics.This feature also allows many different sling-mounting options for the individual users. Any sling adapter that fits on the AR buffer tube should work. This adapter is easy to install without modification to your AK-47, AK-74, AKM and with no need to permanently alter the stock tang.
The Rifle Dynamics RDAK to M-4 stock Adapter is designed by Rifle Dynamics and made in the USA!
Buffer tube, castle nut, end plate and buttstock sold separately.
Stock Adapter will not fit:
◦Milled receiver
◦Chinese guns (Norinco MAK 90, NHM-91, Polytech, B West) Etc.
◦PSL
◦Yugo
◦Any side/under folder stocked rifle, any receiver with stock tang removed.
Although not designed for it, we have been told this adapter does work with certain shotguns.
Our stock adapter will work with both Mil Spec and Commercial buffer tubes.
